trans-unit.source: Creates the theme-specific look for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: Skapar temat leta efter [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: The actual appearance of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> is dependent on which theme is active on the user's system.
trans-unit.target: Det faktiska utseendet på <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>är beroende av vilket tema är aktiv på användarens system.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The properties of this class allow [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] to set the appearance based on the current theme.
trans-unit.target: Tillåt att egenskaperna för den här klassen [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] att ställa in hur baserat på aktuella tema.

trans-unit.source: In XAML usage, a ButtonChrome object element can also have child content, which can be a single <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> that sets the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I XAML-användning, elementet ButtonChrome objekt också ha underordnat innehåll, vilket kan vara en enskild <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>som anger den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>
